          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2019-02-25T21:48:20Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Disarm Hizballah Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Director of National Intelligence to prepare a National Intelligence Estimate on Hizballah which shall include assessments of: (1) Hizballah's tactical capabilities and rocket arsenal, (2) the United Nations Interim Force in Lebanon (UNIFIL), (3) international operations that support Hizballah's network, (4) Hizballah's interference in Middle East conflicts, and (5) Hizballah's fund raising and fund use in territories where UNIFIL operates. </p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-04-17T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
